OL,3,CFootball club announces 'brilliant'
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound upgrade to stadium
OL,6,FChristmas has come a day early for
OL,7,Ffans of Brighton and Hove Albion with
OL,8,Fnews that the club's facilities are
OL,9,Fexpanding.
OL,11,FIt's following its success in recent
OL,12,Fseasons with multimillion pound
OL,13,Finvestments and a larger capacity at
OL,14,Fthe Amex Stadium.
OL,16,FThe Terrace, the new fan zone at the
OL,17,FAmerican Express Stadium will open in
OL,18,Fthe spring and will complete the first
OL,19,Fphase of a further #40m worth of
OL,20,Finvestment in a range of improvements.
