OL,3,CFootball club announces 'brilliant'
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound upgrade to stadium
OL,6,FThe fan zone will offer capacity for
OL,7,Fup to 1000 fans in the colder months
OL,8,Fand the ability to expand outdoors and
OL,9,Fcater for up to 2000 in warmer months
OL,10,F- making it the biggest in the Premier
OL,11,FLeague.
OL,13,FDeputy chairman and chief executive
OL,14,FPaul Barber said, "I know our fans are
OL,15,Flooking forward to the opening of the
OL,16,Fnew fan zone and are extremely excited
OL,17,Fto see these plans come to life.
OL,19,F"It is another incredibly generous
OL,20,Finvestment by our chairman Tony Bloom.
