OL,3,CFootball club announces 'brilliant'
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound upgrade to stadium
OL,6,F"The Terrace will provide a brilliant
OL,7,Faddition to the matchday experience,
OL,8,Fas a place to meet friends before and
OL,9,Fafter matches, watch live sport in a
OL,10,Fmodern space, and enjoy a wide variety
OL,11,Fof food and drink offerings.
OL,13,F"We will also be looking to utilise
OL,14,FThe Terrace for a range of different
OL,15,Fevents and occasions in between
OL,16,Fmatches too, providing a fantastic new
OL,17,Fvenue for fans, the community and
OL,18,Fvisitors to the city to enjoy.
