OL,3,CFootball club announces 'brilliant'
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound upgrade to stadium
OL,6,F"We will be sharing further details
OL,7,Fbetween now and the spring, such as
OL,8,Fopening times and food offerings, but
OL,9,Fwe will work with the best local
OL,10,FSussex suppliers to provide a great
OL,11,Frange of options."
OL,13,FPhase two of the scheme will see a new-
OL,14,Flook and redeveloped club store,
OL,15,Fspanning across two levels.
OL,17,FThe store and Dick's Bar will close
OL,18,Fafter the Arsenal match on 4 January
OL,19,F2025, to begin the work, but a new
OL,20,Ftemporary store will open in Bennett's
OL,21,FField.
