OL,3,CFootball club announces 'brilliant'
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound upgrade to stadium
OL,6,FThe club museum will also relocate to
OL,7,Fa permanent base in the city centre in
OL,8,F2026/27, with further details being
OL,9,Fannounced in the spring of 2025.
OL,11,FPhase three of the project will see an
OL,12,Fadditional 1901 Club area added to the
OL,13,Fnorth stand, which will help boost
OL,14,Fcapacity at the Amex to 32,500 and is
OL,15,Fdue to open in time for the 2026/27
OL,16,Fseason.
