OL,3,CFootball club announces 'brilliant'
OL,4,Cmulti-million pound upgrade to stadium
OL,6,FThe new hospitality area will offer an
OL,7,Farea for home fans only, aimed at
OL,8,Fthose fans who want to be at the heart
OL,9,Fof the atmosphere and show their
OL,10,Fsupport for the team.
OL,12,FOther works planned will include the
OL,13,Fintroduction of safe standing in the
OL,14,FNorth Stand, taking place in 2025,
OL,15,Fwhich the club recently confirmed, and
OL,16,Fin 2027 the relocation of away
OL,17,Fsupporters into the south-west corner
OL,18,Fof the Amex.
